{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a7d578d6b3","title":"关于增产节约的讲话（纪录稿）","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"972d6abb82","index":0,"year":1955,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"a7d578d6b3","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"发言","id":"e23dcf99fa","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui3","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1949-1957卷）（1968年武汉版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui3a.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"357d321458","type":"title","text":"关于增产节约的讲话（纪录稿）","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a7d578d6b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cfa1e08ed7","type":"paragraph","text":"我们是人口众多经济落后的大国，经济水平生活水平均很低，建设社会主义，十五年内是过渡时期，中心是工业化，打物质基础。在现有条件下，继续贯彻党的艰苦奋斗传统。资金唯一来源靠自己积累。第一个五年十个指头，只做了一个。二、三个五年资金需要更大，不厉行节约无法完成任务。如果非生产建设投资突出了，会破坏工农联盟和全国团结，农民为什么不进城？十五年内，不可能样样现代化，样样社会主义。是打基础阶段。非重点建设，非近代技术装备的工厂，第一个五年感到困难，第二第三个更要大。削国防不可能，削行政人员，也非安置生产，非加强生产不可。不可设想削减建设国防人员解决问题。只有全面节约解决问题。","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a7d578d6b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d2f62aa0a8","type":"paragraph","text":"过去认识不深，贯彻不透。如工厂，福利设施均社会主义设施。已无福利可增加。先抓生产、开工。","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a7d578d6b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8621a94e3b","type":"paragraph","text":"农场也太近代化了。牛场 120 万平方米，先进社会。","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a7d578d6b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"47c0536c1b","type":"paragraph","text":"工房、宿舍、高楼、大厦，百把万，住不起。长春汽车厂、乌拉尔厂，宿舍太漂亮了。厨房，西太后出来也要说话了。这是不了解建设困难，忘记传统，违背工业化方针及与农民共艰苦患难的精神。","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a7d578d6b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2bb91ddf1c","type":"paragraph","text":"生产和生活不平衡。节约为了增加积累。","index":5,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a7d578d6b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"16634f925d","type":"paragraph","text":"一、除近代化技术设备以及和设备必要配合的厂房（国外的按国外设计，国内的按可能削减），其它一律降低造价。和延安窑洞看齐，办公室、教室、农场、宿舍、车站等按过渡时期标准，用十五年、二十年。一律砖木结构，甚至土坯子，竹泥墙。","index":6,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a7d578d6b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5138664df8","type":"paragraph","text":"一类是现有大城市，可以砖木。","index":7,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a7d578d6b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2a4c125cf6","type":"paragraph","text":"二类新的单独城市、厂矿，要用土坯。","index":8,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a7d578d6b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3c26d33646","type":"paragraph","text":"办公室、学校 50—70 元","index":9,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a7d578d6b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e40003cb19","type":"paragraph","text":"宿舍 20—50 元","index":10,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a7d578d6b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3360f034fc","type":"paragraph","text":"不同宿舍不同房租。","index":11,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a7d578d6b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fb9343294d","type":"paragraph","text":"仓库 40—50 元","index":12,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a7d578d6b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dc0647cf53","type":"paragraph","text":"车站 50—70 元","index":13,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a7d578d6b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"37c075c7c7","type":"paragraph","text":"首都盖大楼装样子，须国务院批准。","index":14,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a7d578d6b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"711804db1e","type":"paragraph","text":"工程部六—八月拟出标准。","index":15,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a7d578d6b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a5f881db7f","type":"paragraph","text":"二、新建工厂、铁道、农场、福利、设施，根据生产、利润、业务的情况，逐年设施。先抓重点，如宿舍、卫生所无利润以前不建设。不可一下子社会主义，是远景，不是一下子社会主义。首先礼堂不可搞。","index":16,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a7d578d6b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bba620d3d5","type":"paragraph","text":"三、新建企业其它方面厉行节约。轻工业至多一年的筹备机关，以前筹备由部局直接筹备。","index":17,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a7d578d6b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7ba75cee24","type":"paragraph","text":"设计，照标准。重工业部门到苏联的人太多。","index":18,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a7d578d6b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0a4a55692c","type":"paragraph","text":"实习生的待遇要降低。","index":19,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a7d578d6b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f0f78153e6","type":"paragraph","text":"每个环节，严加控制。厂内办公室，沙发一律不准，也不买收音机。不要厂长和职工生活脱离太远。","index":20,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a7d578d6b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"86a3028818","type":"paragraph","text":"四、现有新城，计划均要修改，不要搞社会主义化，要利用旧城。工业要相当疏散。","index":21,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a7d578d6b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cbb9131b9c","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）不搞高大建筑。一层两层。","index":22,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a7d578d6b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b5bd18e49b","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）非工业集中的城市，根本不建城市。如职工用水，可用地下水，用自来水者公共使用水龙头。","index":23,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a7d578d6b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9e482499b8","type":"paragraph","text":"马路要，绿化面积慢慢来。","index":24,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a7d578d6b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"463cc45b34","type":"paragraph","text":"先工业化，后“社会主义化”。二十年后，再用新规划。","index":25,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a7d578d6b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c432cf4715","type":"paragraph","text":"五、今年准备建筑的高楼大厂，未动工的一律停止。","index":26,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a7d578d6b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b0c3d5c738","type":"paragraph","text":"六、地质勘探：","index":27,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a7d578d6b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"22ed1f7179","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）勘探量不必增加。","index":28,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a7d578d6b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1a616bbbf4","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）希望增加的，增加 50％工作量。","index":29,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a7d578d6b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"10e90c8565","type":"paragraph","text":"七、建筑部六、七、八个月交出标准。","index":30,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a7d578d6b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"02107422da","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）生产方面：","index":31,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a7d578d6b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a41b92cdf2","type":"paragraph","text":"1．降低成本：工业 6％加到 7.5％；铁路 2.5——3.5％；商业 2.9——13.9％；","index":32,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a7d578d6b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"046487d215","type":"paragraph","text":"2．节约原料，轻工业、棉花、卷烟量。","index":33,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a7d578d6b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"59c9c82177","type":"paragraph","text":"3．重工业完成新产品试制计划，上半年 49％，不及一半。","index":34,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a7d578d6b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dcb64fe48d","type":"paragraph","text":"4．一律停止收新工人，先内部清理调整，现在都核不清。现在人多了。","index":35,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a7d578d6b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d8fd66493b","type":"paragraph","text":"5．每一环节，直至清理垃圾。鞍钢月搞五万吨钢铁，指标到车间。","index":36,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a7d578d6b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"49d272fac8","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）生活消费：","index":37,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a7d578d6b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9a7e2d35f8","type":"paragraph","text":"1．除招待外宾外，一律只供清茶一杯，一律不请客、会餐。","index":38,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a7d578d6b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ff840b9836","type":"paragraph","text":"2．办公室不买沙发，首长办公室，两个小沙发，用会议桌。","index":39,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a7d578d6b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9a7015b535","type":"paragraph","text":"3．公文表报节约，非国家统计局批不可发。","index":40,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a7d578d6b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9bf54b1827","type":"paragraph","text":"4．减少汽车使用。","index":41,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"a7d578d6b3","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":152,"end":150}}}},"__N_SSG":true}